cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SI 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with natural language processing and word embeddings. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) because it uses neural network methods and deals with vector representations. Additionally, it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) because it deals with neural networks, and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) because it deals with word co-occurrences.
